1 0 0 1 50 772 Tm (This folder contains ready-to-use deployment files for hosting Intratrade on AWS EC2.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 758 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 744 Tm (## Files) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 730 Tm (- `deploy/aws/intratrade.service`: systemd service for Streamlit app) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 716 Tm (- `deploy/aws/chandudevopai.shop.nginx.conf`: nginx reverse proxy config) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 702 Tm (- `deploy/aws/iam-policy-s3.json`: IAM policy template for S3 access) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 688 Tm (- `deploy/aws/deploy.sh`: one-shot setup script \(Ubuntu\)) Tj
