1 0 0 1 50 660 Tm (- `deploy/streamlit/config.toml`: streamlit server config for reverse proxy mode) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 646 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 632 Tm (## Quick steps \(manual\)) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 618 Tm (1. Copy streamlit config:) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 604 Tm (   - `cp deploy/streamlit/config.toml .streamlit/config.toml`) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 590 Tm (2. Install service:) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 576 Tm (   - `sudo cp deploy/aws/intratrade.service /etc/systemd/system/`) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 562 Tm (   - `sudo systemctl daemon-reload && sudo systemctl enable --now intratrade`) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 548 Tm (3. Install nginx vhost:) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 534 Tm (   - Ubuntu/Debian:) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 520 Tm (     - `sudo cp deploy/aws/chandudevopai.shop.nginx.conf /etc/nginx/sites-available/chandudevopai.shop.conf`) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 506 Tm (     - `sudo ln -s /etc/nginx/sites-available/chandudevopai.shop.conf /etc/nginx/sites-enabled/`) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 492 Tm (   - Amazon Linux 2023:) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 478 Tm (     - `sudo cp deploy/aws/chandudevopai.shop.nginx.conf /etc/nginx/conf.d/chandudevopai.shop.conf`) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 464 Tm (   - `sudo nginx -t && sudo systemctl reload nginx`) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 450 Tm (4. Issue SSL cert:) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 436 Tm (   - `sudo certbot --nginx -d chandudevopai.shop -d www.chandudevopai.shop`) Tj
